Agriculture Cabinet Secretary Peter Munya is at the centre of the storm as he implements various critical policies to help in the attainment of the Agriculture Sector Transformation Strategy 2020-2030. The agriculture sector is once again in the news, with various players being on a collision course instead of working together. This time round, the noise is coming from the leading sectors – tea, horticulture, sugar and coffee.
